lastfm.summary: A cover of Toto - Africa featuring "Weird Al" Yankovic. Features on Weezer (Teal Album) In December 2017 a Twitter account called @weezerafrica started a campaign for Weezer to cover Africa. In May 2018 Weezer responded by covering Rosanna by Toto instead. Eventually in September 2018 Weezer collaborated with "Weird Al" Yankovic to cover Africa. Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Africa
